# NAME: MissAV
# AUTHOR: zijinan
# REPO: https://github.com/zijinan/Loon-rule
# UPDATED: 2026-05-26
# FORMAT: Quantumult X / QX
# DESC: MissAV 主站、视频 CDN、封面预览、推荐接口走 PROXY；常见广告/跳转域名 REJECT。

# MissAV main sites
HOST-SUFFIX,missav.ws,PROXY
HOST-SUFFIX,missav.live,PROXY
HOST-SUFFIX,missav.ai,PROXY
HOST-SUFFIX,missav.com,PROXY

# MissAV video / image / preview CDN
HOST-SUFFIX,surrit.com,PROXY
HOST-SUFFIX,fourhoi.com,PROXY

# MissAV recommendation API
HOST,client-rapi-missav.recombee.com,PROXY
HOST-SUFFIX,recombee.com,PROXY

# Optional Cloudflare verification helper.
# Enable only if Cloudflare verification loops.
# HOST-SUFFIX,cloudflare.com,PROXY

# Ads / redirect / tracking
HOST-SUFFIX,tsyndicate.com,REJECT
HOST-SUFFIX,rallytrck.website,REJECT
HOST-SUFFIX,bluetrafficstream.com,REJECT
HOST-SUFFIX,myavlive.com,REJECT
HOST-SUFFIX,keepshare.org,REJECT
